OL,3,CError sees private patients given
OL,4,Cexpensive prescriptions for free
OL,6,FSome private patients in Jersey are
OL,7,Freceiving high-cost prescriptions for
OL,8,Ffree due to an admin error.
OL,10,FFrom Tuesday 1 October, they will have
OL,11,Fto pick up the bill for this
OL,12,Fmedication once again as the
OL,13,FGovernment is currently being charged
OL,14,Finstead.
OL,16,FJersey's Health Minister, Deputy Tom
OL,17,FBinet, says it is unclear how long
OL,18,Fthis has been going on for and
OL,19,Fconfirms it is against the law.
