OL,3,CError sees private patients given
OL,4,Cexpensive prescriptions for free
OL,6,FA new electronic system introduced in
OL,7,FMay flagged the issue.
OL,9,FITV News has asked how much taxpayers'
OL,10,Fmoney will have been lost due to this
OL,11,Fproblem and is waiting for a response.
OL,13,FThe Electronic Prescribing and
OL,14,FMedicines Administration (EPMA) system
OL,15,Fwas brought in at the start of May to
OL,16,Freduce pharmacy waiting times and
OL,17,Fimprove patient safety.
