OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1725902451
OL,3,CError sees private patients given
OL,4,Cexpensive prescriptions for free
OL,6,F"So all we are doing is saying from
OL,7,Fthe first of October, we are going to
OL,8,Frevert to what we should have been
OL,9,Fdoing all along.
OL,11,F"We may look at prescription prices
OL,12,Foverall in the future but for now, we
OL,13,Fneed to be where we need to be by law."
OL,15,FA joint statement with Health and
OL,16,FCommunity Services (HSC) adds: "HCS
OL,17,Fand the Minister acted quickly, and in
OL,18,FJune of this year, to review the
OL,19,Fsituation.
